	    		        <li class="byline">
	        	By <span class="author"><a href="https://ares-sc.org/author/k4lle/" rel="author">Pete K4LLE</a></span><span class="entry-cat"> in <span class="terms"><a class="term term-category term-5" href="https://ares-sc.org/category/latest-news/">Latest News</a></span></span>	        </li>
